{"tid":1332591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[7.21 緊急] 和理非 之必要戰術 (公開)","createTime":"2019-07-19T10:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T13:51:41.000Z","uid":81385,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"035d4e0916d3fffb88e8419bdaa40bcf1d290cce","tid":1332591,"uid":81385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T10:51:25.000Z","msg":"(本post只講<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非</span></strong>遊行，義士唔使跟但希望可以互相support保護)<br />\n1. 灣仔終點係樽頸位，好難散<br />\n2. 預計民陣會學7.1咁繼續行，人多就係力量，勇武請保護群眾!!!<br />\n3. <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非請備普通gear</span></strong> (口罩, N95, 帽/太陽擋(開放式眼罩，唔好著短袖，足夠水，食物，自攜急救包(aeon $12有個好廢的可以用) 唔係叫你上前線，係用來自救<br />\n和理非記住出煙即走，慢慢走咪人踩人，事後可選擇升裝上前線<br />\n4. 後生但係有負擔未能上前線嘅人請係隊中成立撤退救援隊，萬一有事，<strong>請協助一家大細老弱婦孺離開</strong>，民陣係唔夠人應付，要大家幫手!!!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em>請</em>幫手推post ，share去邊都得!!!!"},{"pid":"a724d41b8aa1a2cb2d0283e014f54e645fe9fa08","tid":1332591,"uid":258377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T22:11:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">推哂d 有用嘅post 上嚟， 三毛死撚開DLLM<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n721 15:00 維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a2944206f0befa85e279c22afb00985f9ae310ab","tid":1332591,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T22:13:40.000Z","msg":"其實最好和理非都買埋豬咀防身<br />\n200蚊隨時可以做滅火隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no